+ Unpivot Columns\ninto Rows
++ What is Unpivoting?
+++ Wide format → Long format
++++_ Columns become rows
++++_ Reverse of pivoting
++ SQL UNPIVOT Clause
+++ Specify value column name
+++ Specify name column
+++ List columns to unpivot
++++_ ... FOR month IN (jan, feb, mar)
+++ INCLUDE NULLS option
++++_ Default excludes nulls
+++ Custom aliases for column names
-- Use Cases
---_ Normalize wide data
---_ Prepare for aggregation
---_ ML pipeline input format
-- Requires
---_ Databricks Runtime 12.2 LTS+
